{"tid":2141263,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"美國準備收香港金融業皮？","createTime":"2020-08-05T13:53:41.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-06T20:58:55.000Z","uid":149494,"like":12,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"72fe8ecccfc83708aa766e09e3147da3f844088e","tid":2141263,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:53:41.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542050-20200805.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542050-20200805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=0%2B8fQjowpNY%2FdBz24eqX%2Fy%2B6%2F41ZtH0%2FHUJlQhqDsdc%3D&h=14d5f135\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1542050-20200805.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=755c8371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1542050-20200805.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n美國總統特朗普表示，當美國取消對香港的特殊待遇地位後，美國的證券交易所將會取得更多業務。<br />\n<br />\n特朗普接受《霍士新聞》訪問時表示，過往美國給予香港太多誘因，令香港從紐約證券交易所、納斯達克等奪走大部分業務，但香港失去美方給予的特殊待遇地位後，將不會是一個成功的證券交易地。<br />\n<br />\n另外，特朗普又指，有可能在白宮內發表獲共和黨全國黨代表提名的演說，認為是一個最容易的選項，但有關計劃未進一步確定。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"34e7e376f570385e33acc25d09917757b0c1fab5","tid":2141263,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-05T13:54:14.000Z","msg":"香港金融撚何去何從？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/ass